data.description: **BACK ON MARKET BUYERS FINANCING FELL THROUGH. HERE IS YOUR CHANCE!** This is the home you've been looking for! This beautiful Balboa model was built in 2021 and has amazing upgrades. As soon as you enter you will be greeted by gorgeous porcelain floors. Additional upgrades include 42" shaker style kitchen cabinets, waterfall quartz counters and a whole house water filtration system. This home sits on an oversized lot with room for a pool, playground and more! Offered at an affordable price and no waiting for new construction! Situated in Silverwood inside Ave Maria, this home is close to the town center where you can find many amenities. Such as restaurants, shopping, Dr.'s offices and more. Town features a water park, dog parks, play ground, sports fields, bike/jogging paths, gas station, Publix and more.
